						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="italic">Pillar of the maṇṭapa in front of the Yellamma temple.</hi></p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">A.D. 1538.</hi></p>						

						<p>This inscription dated in <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1460, Viḷambi, Āshāḍha Śu. 5, Monday,</hi> states that <hi rend="bold">Virayya,</hi> son of <hi rend="bold">Daṇḍige Mallayya</hi> of <hi rend="bold">Dvagiri</hi> built the gateway (of the village) The details of the date correspond to <hi rend="bold">A.D. 1538, July 1, Monday.</hi></p>						

